    Overview

    Meet the CloudAlign Pillow, crafted for deep, supported sleep in any position. Whether you're a side, back, or stomach sleeper, the 3-zone contour design delivers targeted neck lift, pressure relief, and full-body alignment.


    Powered by our SwitchFit™ dual-height system and made with fast-drying, washable materials, CloudAlign adapts to your sleep style. There is no bunching, flipping, or fuss.

    Please note that if you order one pillowcase, the pillow will ship with the pillowcase on the pillow.

    Care

    The pillow itself is not machine washable because it does not hold smells or bacteria. It is hypoallergenic memory foam. If you order a pillowcase, the pillowcases are fully machine washable and dryer safe. Also, if you order a pillowcase, it will ship on the pillow already.

    Materials

    OEKO-TEX® Certified Cover: Hypoallergenic, breathable, and gentle on skin.


    CloudSoft Core: Shape-retaining memory foam that’s durable and flexible for enduring support.

    FAQ

    How does the dual height system work?

    One side is 3.5 inches high, the other is 4.3 inches. Switch the pillow to choose your preferred neck support height.


    Is this pillow good for side, back, and stomach sleepers?

    Yes. CloudAlign’s contoured zones adapt to all sleep positions — side, back, and stomach — providing targeted support and alignment.


    Will it flatten over time?

    No. CloudAlign is made with shape-retaining memory foam that stay supportive.


    Is it safe for sensitive skin?

    Absolutely. The OEKO-TEX® certified cover is hypoallergenic, breathable, and skin-friendly.


    Does the memory foam smell?
    When you first open your sleeply pillow, you may notice a slight “new foam” or “fresh out of the box” scent. This is completely normal and temporary.

    Our pillow uses high-quality foam materials that are compressed and sealed for shipping. When the pillow is unboxed, the materials naturally release trapped air from packaging — a process commonly referred to as off-gassing.

    The scent is not harmful and typically dissipates on its own within 24–72 hours

    Is the smell toxic or dangerous?

    No. The initial scent does not mean your pillow is toxic or unsafe.

    The materials used in the sleeply pillow meet strict safety standards and are designed for everyday sleep use. The smell comes from the manufacturing and packaging process, not from anything being released into the pillow while you sleep.

    Once aired out, the scent fades quickly and does not return.

    How can I get rid of the smell faster?

    If you’d like to speed things up, we recommend:

    • Removing the pillow from its packaging immediately

    • Letting it air out in a well-ventilated room

    • Allowing 24–72 hours for full freshness

    Using a pillowcase and normal room airflow is usually all it takes.

    Frequently asked questions

    How does the dual-height system work?

    Each side of the pillow is different in height, one higher and one lower. Flip the pillow to find the support level that feels best for your neck and sleep position.

    Is this pillow good for side, back, and stomach sleepers?

    Yes. CloudAlign is designed for all sleep styles. Its ergonomic shape adapts to side, back, and stomach sleepers by providing targeted lift and pressure relief where you need it most.

    Will it flatten over time?

    No. CloudAlign is made with shape-retaining materials that keep their support even after frequent washing.

    Is it safe for sensitive skin?

    Absolutely. The OEKO-TEX® certified cover is hypoallergenic, breathable, and gentle on skin.
